样细致</description></item><item><title>爱邻舍，从践行力所能及的小事起——记人生第一场义卖会</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E7%88%B1%E9%82%BB%E8%88%8D%E4%BB%8E%E8%B7%B5%E8%A1%8C%E5%8A%9B%E6%89%80%E8%83%BD%E5%8F%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B%E8%B5%B7-%E8%AE%B0%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Jan 2016 07:13:41 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E7%88%B1%E9%82%BB%E8%88%8D%E4%BB%8E%E8%B7%B5%E8%A1%8C%E5%8A%9B%E6%89%80%E8%83%BD%E5%8F%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B%E8%B5%B7-%E8%AE%B0%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80/</guid><description>文/艳青 如果没有雾霾，我们感受不到在阳光灿烂的户外深呼一口气的喜悦与感恩；如果没有有关部门对教会格外的关注和逼迫，我可能仍然生活在自己安逸的</description></item><item><title>新年感悟</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E6%84%9F%E6%82%9F-%E6%96%87%E6%9D%A8%E6%B4%8B/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Jan 2016 07:09:34 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E6%84%9F%E6%82%9F-%E6%96%87%E6%9D%A8%E6%B4%8B/</guid><description>文/杨洋 今年的跨年是在恩平师母带领的祷告会中度过的。从来没有觉得一年的开始可以这样庄严、圣洁、有恩典有力量有意义。这一年，虽然教会依然处在这</description></item><item><title>《夏洛特烦恼》与《生活多美好》</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E5%A4%8F%E6%B4%9B%E7%89%B9%E7%83%A6%E6%81%BC%E4%B8%8E%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%A4%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%BD-%E6%96%87%E8%B5%B5%E5%91%A8/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Jan 2016 07:09:14 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E5%A4%8F%E6%B4%9B%E7%89%B9%E7%83%A6%E6%81%BC%E4%B8%8E%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%A4%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%BD-%E6%96%87%E8%B5%B5%E5%91%A8/</guid><description>文/赵周 今年有一部电影特别火，《夏洛特烦恼》。主人公叫夏洛，人到中年一事无成，特烦恼。天降机缘得到返回高中重来一次的机会，他靠着先知先觉，在</description></item><item><title>务求传福音，为神作见证</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E5%8A%A1%E6%B1%82%E4%BC%A0%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3%E4%B8%BA%E7%A5%9E%E4%BD%9C%E8%A7%81%E8%AF%81-%E6%96%87%E5%85%B4%E6%A2%85/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Jan 2016 07:07:31 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E5%8A%A1%E6%B1%82%E4%BC%A0%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3%E4%B8%BA%E7%A5%9E%E4%BD%9C%E8%A7%81%E8%AF%81-%E6%96%87%E5%85%B4%E6%A2%85/</guid><description>&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;
文/兴梅
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我们真的要改变自己，让上帝的光照亮自己的心，使自己的生命能发出来自耶稣的光，所流露出的耶稣的馨香之气能影响到我们的亲人。转变生命是基督徒在亲人面前能为主耶稣所作出的最好见证。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>我愿做传福音的鸽子</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E6%88%91%E6%84%BF%E5%81%9A%E4%BC%A0%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3%E7%9A%84%E9%B8%BD%E5%AD%9012%E6%9C%8823%E6%97%A5%E7%A5%B7%E5%91%8A%E4%BC%9A%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E6%96%87%E5%92%8F%E8%8E%B2/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Jan 2016 07:05:02 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E6%88%91%E6%84%BF%E5%81%9A%E4%BC%A0%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3%E7%9A%84%E9%B8%BD%E5%AD%9012%E6%9C%8823%E6%97%A5%E7%A5%B7%E5%91%8A%E4%BC%9A%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E6%96%87%E5%92%8F%E8%8E%B2/</guid><description>&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;
文/咏莲
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我个人认为传福音是保持灵命成长最好的方式之一，保罗在以弗所书六章15节说：&amp;ldquo;又用平安的福音当作预备走路的鞋穿在脚上。&amp;rdquo;可见福音是走天路的鞋，不传福音就如同走路时没有穿鞋，力量很有限。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>让我们回到那起初的爱—-一个平信徒的户外反思</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E8%AE%A9%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E5%9B%9E%E5%88%B0%E9%82%A3%E8%B5%B7%E5%88%9D%E7%9A%84%E7%88%B1-%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%B9%B3%E4%BF%A1%E5%BE%92%E7%9A%84%E6%88%B7%E5%A4%96%E5%8F%8D%E6%80%9D-%E6%96%87/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Jan 2016 07:02:05 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E8%AE%A9%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E5%9B%9E%E5%88%B0%E9%82%A3%E8%B5%B7%E5%88%9D%E7%9A%84%E7%88%B1-%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%B9%B3%E4%BF%A1%E5%BE%92%E7%9A%84%E6%88%B7%E5%A4%96%E5%8F%8D%E6%80%9D-%E6%96%87/</guid><description>&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;line-height: 20.8px; text-align: center;&#34;&gt;文/刘新明&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;面对新一轮的属灵逼迫，求主使孩子不灰心丧胆，也求主赐给孩子愿意付代价的心。只要所有弟兄姊妹在主里面合一，共同持守神所赐给我们教会的异象，神必与我们同在,人又能拿我们怎么样呢？&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>燕郊小组庆祝圣诞纪实</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E7%87%95%E9%83%8A%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%84%E5%BA%86%E7%A5%9D%E5%9C%A3%E8%AF%9E%E7%BA%AA%E5%AE%9E-%E6%96%87%E9%A6%A8%E8%8A%B3/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Jan 2016 06:58:01 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E7%87%95%E9%83%8A%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%84%E5%BA%86%E7%A5%9D%E5%9C%A3%E8%AF%9E%E7%BA%AA%E5%AE%9E-%E6%96%87%E9%A6%A8%E8%8A%B3/</guid><description>文/馨芳 一个永久纪念的日子&amp;mdash;&amp;mdash;12月25日。两千多年前，在遥远的伯利恒，一家客店里，一位婴孩带着嘹亮的啼哭声降生了。</description></item><item><title>因他活着，生命充满希望一一守望教会香柏与百合花欢庆2015圣诞节记实</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E5%9B%A0%E4%BB%96%E6%B4%BB%E7%9D%80%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%85%85%E6%BB%A1%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%88%E6%9C%9B%E6%95%99%E4%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%9F%8F%E4%B8%8E%E7%99%BE%E5%90%88/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Jan 2016 06:57:15 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E5%9B%A0%E4%BB%96%E6%B4%BB%E7%9D%80%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%85%85%E6%BB%A1%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%88%E6%9C%9B%E6%95%99%E4%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%9F%8F%E4%B8%8E%E7%99%BE%E5%90%88/</guid><description>经过一段时间的精心准备，北京守望教会香柏团契与百合花小组的弟兄姊妹于12月23日一起喜迎2015年圣诞节。 除了一棵圣诞树，小小会场几无修饰，</description></item><item><title>圣诞活动杂感</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E5%9C%A3%E8%AF%9E%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E6%9D%82%E6%84%9F-%E6%96%87%E9%99%88%E4%BA%AE/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Jan 2016 06:56:50 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E5%9C%A3%E8%AF%9E%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E6%9D%82%E6%84%9F-%E6%96%87%E9%99%88%E4%BA%AE/</guid><description>文/陈亮 2015年12月25日晚，冰霞、刘优、雪芹、好智、赵周等组联合部分诗班成员举行了&amp;ldquo;圣诞歌曲联谊会&amp;rdquo;。我参加了</description></item><item><title>世纪城小组圣诞活动小记</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%84%E5%9C%A3%E8%AF%9E%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%B0%8F%E8%AE%B0-%E6%96%87%E7%8E%89%E5%8D%8E/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Jan 2016 06:55:59 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%84%E5%9C%A3%E8%AF%9E%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%B0%8F%E8%AE%B0-%E6%96%87%E7%8E%89%E5%8D%8E/</guid><description>文/玉华 又是一年圣诞来临，今年的圣诞怎么过？ 出去发福音单张？邀请慕道友聚会？小组弟兄姐妹过个嗨皮的佳期聚会？大家七嘴八舌，最后统一为圣诞见证</description></item><item><title>给通州小组弟兄姊妹的一封信</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E7%BB%99%E9%80%9A%E5%B7%9E%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%84%E5%BC%9F%E5%85%84%E5%A7%8A%E5%A6%B9%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%B0%81%E4%BF%A1/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Jan 2016 06:54:53 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E7%BB%99%E9%80%9A%E5%B7%9E%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%84%E5%BC%9F%E5%85%84%E5%A7%8A%E5%A6%B9%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%B0%81%E4%BF%A1/</guid><description>亲爱的通州小组的弟兄姊妹们：刚刚过去的圣诞节，我们都被爱和礼物所充满、所包围。活动结束当天晚上，我们在微信群里感谢彼此的付出，那天晚上我失眠</description></item><item><title>圣诞夜 传福音 清枫小组</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E5%9C%A3%E8%AF%9E%E5%A4%9C-%E4%BC%A0%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3-%E6%B8%85%E6%9E%AB%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%84/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Jan 2016 06:52:38 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E5%9C%A3%E8%AF%9E%E5%A4%9C-%E4%BC%A0%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3-%E6%B8%85%E6%9E%AB%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%84/</guid><description>一起出去传那平安的福音（文/樊春良） &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; 临近圣诞节，开始筹划小组的圣诞活动，首选的还是去地铁口发福音单张。小组聚会时，说了想法，弟兄姊妹都同意</description></item><item><title>愿你的国降临</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E6%84%BF%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%8D%E4%B8%B4-%E6%96%87%E6%99%93%E5%B3%B0-%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%88/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Jan 2016 06:49:51 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E6%84%BF%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%8D%E4%B8%B4-%E6%96%87%E6%99%93%E5%B3%B0-%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%88/</guid><description>&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;
文/晓峰 牧师
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;祷告是对上帝的亲近、是对上帝心意的寻求、是对上帝恩典的寻求、而且祷告是来参与上帝自己的计划，所以祷告更多是来明白上帝的心意，有份于上帝的工作。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>为所信的福音齐心努力</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E4%B8%BA%E6%89%80%E4%BF%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3%E9%BD%90%E5%BF%83%E5%8A%AA%E5%8A%9B-%E6%96%87%E8%A2%81%E7%81%B5%E4%BC%A0%E9%81%93/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Jan 2016 06:43:59 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E4%B8%BA%E6%89%80%E4%BF%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3%E9%BD%90%E5%BF%83%E5%8A%AA%E5%8A%9B-%E6%96%87%E8%A2%81%E7%81%B5%E4%BC%A0%E9%81%93/</guid><description>&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;
文/袁灵传道
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在新的一年我们需要求主除去我们等着平安了再传福音的观念，除去聚会正常才能传福音的观念，除去我们现在会吓跑慕道友的观念。求主破碎我们错误的观念，求主赐给我们正确的信心。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>以素常的心面对为义受苦</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E4%BB%A5%E7%B4%A0%E5%B8%B8%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%83%E9%9D%A2%E5%AF%B9%E4%B8%BA%E4%B9%89%E5%8F%97%E8%8B%A6-2015%E5%B9%B4%E7%BB%88%E6%84%9F%E6%81%A9%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E6%96%87%E5%AD%99/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Jan 2016 06:38:45 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2016/01/12/%E4%BB%A5%E7%B4%A0%E5%B8%B8%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%83%E9%9D%A2%E5%AF%B9%E4%B8%BA%E4%B9%89%E5%8F%97%E8%8B%A6-2015%E5%B9%B4%E7%BB%88%E6%84%9F%E6%81%A9%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E6%96%87%E5%AD%99/</guid><description>&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;
文/孙毅长老
&lt;/p&gt;
